# =============================================================================
# Telegram Bot — PM Escalation Notifications (US-7.1)
# =============================================================================
# 1. Create a bot via @BotFather on Telegram → /newbot → copy the token below.
# 2. Start a chat with your bot (or add it to a group), then find your chat ID:
#    curl "https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates"
#    Look for "chat":{"id":<number>} in the response.
# 3. Copy this file to .env and fill in the real values.

TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=123456789:AABBccDDeeFFggHHiiJJkkLLmmNNooP
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=987654321
